<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-green);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">MEPH</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Electrical</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">From the intake to the last light fitting, the electrical package touches every part of a building — and every other trade depends on it landing right. We self-deliver LV power, distribution, lighting and EV charging, tested and certified to BS 7671, with one accountable team from first fix to final certificate.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Electrical →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What we deliver</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Electrical,<br>self-delivered.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span>Scope</span></h4><ul><li>LV power &amp; distribution boards</li><li>Switchgear &amp; sub-mains</li><li>Lighting &amp; emergency lighting</li><li>Small power &amp; containment</li><li>EV charging infrastructure</li><li>Testing, inspection &amp; certification</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span>Standards &amp; compliance</span></h4><ul><li>BS 7671 — IET Wiring Regs (18th Edition)</li><li>Building Regulations Part P</li><li>BS 5266 — emergency lighting</li><li>CDM 2015 across every package</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Are installations certified?</summary><p>Yes. Every installation is designed, tested and certified to BS 7671 (18th Edition), backed by AMPM Group's accreditations and a full set of test certificates.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you install EV charging?</summary><p>Yes. We deliver EV charging from single bays to multi-bay car parks, including the distribution-board and supply upgrades the load usually requires.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you work in occupied buildings?</summary><p>Yes. We phase work around live buildings using out-of-hours isolations, temporary supplies and floor-by-floor sequencing so the building keeps running.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">Part of MEPH</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Explore the full<br>package.</h2></div><div class="sectorrow reveal in"><a class="sector" href="/meph/">MEPH overview</a><a class="sector" href="/meph/mechanical-hvac/">Mechanical &amp; HVAC</a><a class="sector" href="/meph/public-health/">Public Health</a><a class="sector" href="/meph/data-infrastructure/">Data &amp; IT infrastructure</a></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">The other three lines</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One contractor,<br>four service l